 class="icon"><svg class="icon-email" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 13.32"><path d="M20 .1V0H0v.1l10 6.5L20 .1z"></path><path d="M10 9.22A1.23 1.23 0 019.35 9L0 3v10.32h20V3l-9.35 6a1.23 1.23 0 01-.65.22z"></path></svg></div></a><a class="print"><div class="icon"><svg class="icon-print" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 18.31"><rect x="5.44" width="9.12" height="3.66"></rect><rect x="4.51" y="13.35" width="11.02" height="4.96"></rect><path d="M20,15.14H17.62V10.93H2.38v4.21H0V5.75H20ZM17.43,7.38a.94.94,0,1,0,.94.94.94.94,0,0,0-.94-.94Z"></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div></div></article></main><div class="ad-unit"><div class="htl-ad htlunit-House_DONATE" data-refresh="auto" data-sizes="0x0:300x250|900x0:728x90|1024x0:970x250" data-unit="House_DONATE" data-prebid="0x0:|900x0:|1024x0:" data-page="article" data-lazy-pixels="350"></div></div><footer class="footer undefinedFooter fade-in" id="footer"><div class="footer__topRow"><ul class="footer__verticalsNav"><li><a href="/the-soapbox">THE SOAPBOX</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/apocalypse-soon">APOCALYPSE SOON</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/sold-short">SOLD SHORT</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/critical-mass">CRITICAL MASS</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/magazine">MAGAZINE</a> <svg class="footerSlash" width="7.52" height="20.67"><line x1="10%" y1="100%" x2="90%" y2="0"></line></svg></li><li><a href="/podcasts">PODCASTS</a></li></ul><ul class="footer__aboutNav"><li><a href="/pages/events">Events</a></li><li><a href="https://w1.buysub.com/servlet/OrdersGateway?cds_mag_code=NRD&amp;cds_page_id=242949&amp;cds_response_key=I0FNRFTR">Donate</a></li><li><a href="https://advertise.newrepublic.com/">Advertise</a></li><li><a href="/pages/subscriber-services">Subscriber Services</a></li><li><a href="/tags/press-release">Press</a></li><li><a href="/pages/about#jobs">Jobs</a></li><li><a href="/pages/contact#submissionGuidelines">Submissions</a></li></ul></div><div class="footer__middleRow"><ul><li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/newrepublic/"><svg class="footer_facebookIcon" aria-label="Facebook" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" overflow="visible"><path d="M0 0h24v24h-7.4v-9.3h3.1l.5-3.7h-3.6V8.5c0-.8.6-1.4 1.4-1.4h2.3V3.7l-2.9-.1c-2.7-.1-4.6 2-4.6 4.4v3H9.7v3.7h3.1V24H0V0z"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/newrepublic/"><svg class="footer__instagramIcon" aria-label="Instagram" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" overflow="visible"><path d="M18.6 0H5.4C2.4 0 0 2.4 0 5.4v13.2c0 3 2.4 5.4 5.4 5.4h13.2c3 0 5.4-2.4 5.4-5.4V5.4c0-3-2.4-5.4-5.4-5.4zM12 18.4c-3.6 0-6.4-2.9-6.4-6.4 0-3.6 2.9-6.4 6.4-6.4 3.6 0 6.4 2.9 6.4 6.4 0 3.6-2.8 6.4-6.4 6.4zm7.4-12.3c-.8 0-1.5-.7-1.5-1.5s.7-1.5 1.5-1.5 1.5.7 1.5 1.5-.6 1.5-1.5 1.5z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4.2"></circle></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://www.twitter.com/newrepublic/"><svg class="footer__twitterIcon" aria-label="Twitter" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"></path></svg></a></li><li><a href="https://flipboard.co